modName: Dragonborn Comes Extended Main Menu Music
summary: Self-mixed Extended Version of Malukah Fenix\'s The Dragonborn Comes as Main Menu Music.
descriptionHtml:
This is a Main Menu song replacement. I mixed some of the different versions of Malukah Fenix\'s amazing rendition of The Dragonborn Comes. It starts off with a very angelic-sounding part of the Morrowind \"aahs\", goes on to the Dragonborn part, then adds piano to the last part of the song, all the way through to the end.

It\'s sort of hard to explain, so check it out, I promise it\'s worth it.

Thanks:
Malukah, for your amazing talent!
JohnB, for the Skyrim Audio Converter
author: Jay33721
